    "asOf": "2021-03-11",
    "date": "2021-05-24T16:23:05Z",
    "text": "NEPA Data Transparency and Accountability Act\n\nThis bill requires federal agencies to annually report on their environmental review activities under the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 (NEPA).\n\nThe agencies must also include the cost of their NEPA activities in the annual reports after the Council on Environmental Quality and the Office of Management and Budget have developed a methodology to assess the comprehensive costs of the NEPA process."
